    />

    <img src="/assets/images/day.png" class="relative z-30 w-full my-10 rounded-xl h-[500px] object-cover transition-opacity duration-500 dark:opacity-0 dark:hidden" />
    <img src="/assets/images/night.png" class="relative z-30 w-full my-10 rounded-xl h-[500px] object-cover transition-opacity duration-500 opacity-0 dark:opacity-100 hidden dark:block" />

    <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Short Bio</h2>
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      Computer Scientist üßëüèª‚Äçüíª focused on machine learning, deep learning, and AI research. Passionate about reinforcement learning, mathematics, and building intelligent systems at scale.
    </p>
    <p
      class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      In my free time, I love swimming, playing basketball, and exploring new places. Growing up in a coastal town, I‚Äôve always been drawn to the sky and the ocean‚Äîand the pictures above remind me of home!
    </p>

    <h2
