      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      If you want to connect with me, feel free to <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/catluong1602/"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-indigo-600 underline">reach out on LinkedIn</a
      >, or you can send me an <a href="mailto:luongcat162002@gmail.com" class="text-indigo-600 underline"
        >email</a
